it.unipd.dei.eis.presentation

Class AsyncExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipd.dei.eis.presentation.AsyncExecutor

  • public class AsyncExecutor
extends Object
    The AsyncExecutor class is the singleton class that executes the controllers. It contains the execute method.
